revision.text:
'''中津神社'''（なかつじんじゃ）は[[神社]]。[[日本]]各地に鎮座する。
*[[中津神社 (愛川町)]] - 神奈川県愛甲郡愛川町鎮座 *[[中津神社 (千早赤阪村)]] - 大阪府南河内郡千早赤阪村鎮座 *中津神社 - 壱岐島壱岐郡の[[名神大社|式内名神大社]] ⇒ [[聖母宮]] **[[中津神社 (壱岐市)]] - 長崎県壱岐市鎮座。上記の[[論社]] *[[中津神社 (中津市)]] - 大分県中津市鎮座 *[[中津神社 (鹿屋市)]] - 鹿児島県鹿屋市鎮座
{{曖昧さ回避}}
{{デフォルトソート:なかつしんしや}}

'''Nakatsu Shrine''' (中津神社)
* {{ill|Nakatsu Shrine (Aikawa Town)|ja|中津神社 (愛川町)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Aikawa Town|ja|愛川町|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Aikō District|ja|愛甲郡|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Kanagawa Prefecture|ja|神奈川県|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Nakatsu Shrine (Chihayaakasaka Village)|ja|中津神社 (千早赤阪村)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Chihayaakasaka Village|ja|千早赤阪村|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Minamikawachi District|ja|南河内郡|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Osaka Prefecture|ja|大阪府|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Nakatsu Shrine (Iki City)|ja|中津神社 (壱岐市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Iki City|ja|壱岐市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Nagasaki Prefecture|ja|長崎県|12=draft|12=draft}}. A {{ill|Shikinai Myōjin Taisha|ja|式内名神大社|fr|Myōjin Taisha|zh|名神大社|12=draft|12=draft}} candidate. * {{ill|Nakatsu Daijingū|ja|中津大神宮|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Nakatsu City|ja|中津市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Ōita Prefecture|ja|大分県|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Nakatsu Shrine (Kanoya City)|ja|中津神社 (鹿屋市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Kanoya City|ja|鹿屋市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Kagoshima Prefecture|ja|鹿児島県|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Related Items == * {{ill|Seibo Shrine|ja|聖母宮|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Iki City, Nagasaki Prefecture. A leading candidate for the Shikinai Myōjin Taisha Nakatsu Shrine. {{citation needed|Nakatsu Shrine}}
